quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,ﾄｰzessemaunﾅ歛kkat
  84,2,Ve ezinet lirabbiha ve hukkat
  84,3,Ve izelﾂｴardu muddet
  84,4,Ve elkat ma fiyha ve tehallet
  84,5,Ve ezinet lirabbiha ve hukkat
  84,6,Ya eyyuhelﾂｴinsanu inneke kadihun ila rabbike kedhan femulakﾄｱyhi
  84,7,Femma men utiye kitabehu biyemiynihi
  84,8,Fesevfe yuhasebu hﾄｱsaben yesiyren
  84,9,Ve yenkalibu ila ehlihi mesruren
  84,10,Ve emma men utiye kitabehu verae zahrihi
  84,11,Fesevfe yedﾂｴu suburen
  84,12,Ve yasla seﾂｴﾄｱyren
  84,13,ﾄｰnnehu kane fiy ehlihi mesruren
  84,14,ﾄｰnnehu zanne en len yehure
  84,15,Bela inne rabbehu kane bihi basﾄｱyren
  84,16,Fela uksimﾃｼ biﾅ淒歹fekﾄｱ
  84,17,Velleyli ve ma veseka
  84,18,Velkameri izetteseka
  84,19,Leterkebunne tabekan ﾂｴan tabekﾄｱn
  84,20,Femalehum la yuﾂｴminune
  84,21,Ve iza kurie ﾂｴaleyhimﾃｼlkurﾂｴanu la yescudune
  84,22,Belilleziyne keferu yukezzibune
  84,23,Vallahu aﾂｴlemu bima yuﾂｴune
  84,24,Febeﾅ淒殃rhﾃｼm biﾂｴazabin eliymin
  84,25,ﾄｰllelleziyne amenu ve ﾂｴamilussalihati lehum erun gayru memnunin